Dialogs.Dialog: All right. What're we gonna talk about？
What？ You want to chat with Rinko, huh？
Oh, you're still awake. Okay. Let's chat.
It's noon, isn't it？ Did you just wake up？
You woke up at this time？ From a nap？
You just woke up？ It's okay, though.
Eh？ You just woke up？ When did you go to bed？
Are you going to bed now？ Your time is reversed, huh？
You're going to bed now？ It's so early.
Good night. Rinko will stay up for a while, though.
Good night. It's time you go to bed, huh？
You're going to bed now？ It's late, huh？
Speaking of which... Ah, never mind.
Do you have anything you wanna ask？
▲主人公＊▲. Just try calling your name！
You're looking forward to our date, right？
Right. We both are looking forward to it.
What does that mean？ It's our date, you know？
Our recent date was great, wasn't it？
Right. I'll wait for the next one, okay？
What？ Rinko was the only one who thought it was great？
Who are you thinking about right now？
Are you expecting something on Valentine's Day？
Hehe. I wonder what I'll do.
What are you gonna do on Christmas？ Spending time with your girlfriend, huh？
Hehe. I want it to arrive soon.
Fine！ Rinko will enjoy her time alone then.
Our anniversary is coming soon. You remembered it, right？
Well, that's just natural. Anyway, I'm happy.
Hey, it's almost your birthday. Are you looking forward to it？
It's almost Rinko's bday. You remembered it, right？
Then Rinko can expect something nice from you, right？
This year will be over soon. Has it been a really wonderful year？
That's right. Because you have Rinko by your side.
Soon, the new semester will start. You want it to come sooner？
Okay. Because you want to see Rinko at school, right？
Nah... We'll get homework and stuff...
Tests are coming up. Have you already studied？
Soon it'll be spring. Do you like spring？
Yeah, I want to see cherry blossoms.
Soon it'll be summer. Do you like summer？
Right. The ocean, the fireworks... We will be so busy.
It's just so hot. Rinko also hates summer.
Soon it'll be fall. Do you like fall？
As a library committee member, fall is best for reading.
It's such a lonesome season. But you aren't lonely, are you？
Soon it'll be winter. Do you like winter？
There are so many winter festivals. Are they really designed for lovers？
What？ You don't like cold weather？
Hey, tell me your favorite color.
Hey, tell me your favorite food.
Yeah, same as Rinko. It's yummy, right？
Huh, really？ Rinko hates it though.
What kind of outfit would you like Rinko to wear？
Then I'll remember that. But don't expect too much.
That's... Are all men like this？
Well, I'll remember this for later, then.
Hey, what kind of movies do you like？
Same as Rinko. We have similar taste, huh？
What would you like to see at the event hall？
They have something like that, too？ I see.
Where would you like to go for a date？
Yeah, same as Rinko. Let's go there together.
Well, if you like it, it's okay.
Well, any place is okay if I go with you.
Hey, if Rinko were an animal, what would Rinko be？
Hehe. Is that so？ A cat？ Nya▼
Same as Rinko. Next time, let's go together.
Such a place exists？ I don't know it.
Hehe. I already knew it. Just wanted a confirmation.
R-Really？ Rinko also loves you so much.
Hey... What part of Rinko do you like？
You're not going to say it, huh？
Hey, do you like it...？ I mean... the kiss.
You admitted it. Rinko also likes it, so we're fine！
Well... Do you like doing skinship？
Well, Rinko likes it, too. Hehe.
I see. You were forcing yourself, huh？
Hey, do you mind people staring when we kiss？
Really？ You are not that reliable...
Geez. At least you should mind a little bit. Well, it's okay, though.
Hey, from now on, let's do many things together, just the two of us.
If it's you, Rinko's answer is okay.
Do you have a dream for your future？
Yeah, it will come true. Rinko will help you with it, too.
Is that so？ Then Rinko will help you think about it, okay？
Hey... Could it be that Rinko is your first love？
Hehe. Yay！ It's the same for Rinko.
I see. Not like I care！
Hey, do you remember the first time we met？
Rinko can't ever forget about it.
No way. I can't believe it.
Do you remember our first date？
Yeah, I was so nervous then.
Hey, do you remember when Rinko confessed to you？
Hehe. That's right. It must be an extremely important moment for you！
You didn't have to ask... Of course, I love you.
Yeah, I love you. Um, I'm so in love with you.
Well. I like red and yellow and the warm-tone colors.
I enjoy the stores that I can look for clothes.
I think I enjoy going to accessory shops.
I like cosmetic stores, I guess. I think they are pretty enjoyable.
I like cute clothes. It's not weird, I hope.
I like neat and feminine clothes. I didn't like them before, though.
I like casual clothes. It's the best when I want to have some fun.
We have talked quite a lot today. Hehe.
We've spent some time talking today.
We didn't talk much today. Let's talk more next time.
Roger that. Wake up on time, all right？
Wake up！ It's time！ Hey, wake up！
Hey, I said "wake up！" Why aren't you waking up！？ Hey！
Ah, sorry. I forgot to wake you up. Hehe.
Here's your last chance. One, two... Wake up！
Roger that. When it's time, I'll call you. Leave it to me.
It's time already. It's a little late though. Hope it's okay.
Hey, it's time. You know what to do, right？ You'd better hurry.
Well, I think you promised to meet someone, right？
Let's play rock-paper- scissors. If you win best out of 3, I'll give you a reward.
All right. Now, starting with rock... Ready？
Hehe. Rinko's victory. Now, you should follow my orders... Kidding.
I lost, huh？ As promised, I'll give you a reward.
Well... This is special for you.
Huh？ You want to quit, eh？
Just look outside and you will know. It's nighttime.
It's in the middle of the night！
Kobayakawa Rinko can tell you that it's midnight.
It's 2 A.M. You're probably getting sleepy.
3 A.M. now. Aren't you going to bed yet？
4 A.M. You're really trying your best, huh？
8 A.M. Are you ready for today？
9 o'clock. Is your brain already awake？
It's noon！ Hey, what will you eat？
1 o'clock. Are you ready for the afternoon？
3 o'clock is time for potato chips！
4 o'clock. Are you tired？ Just keep it up！
5 o'clock. Time to take a breather.
6 o'clock. What are you gonna do now？
7 o'clock. What will your side dishes be？
8 o'clock. What are you doing？ Studying or are you watching TV？
10 o'clock. You aren't sleepy yet, right？
Only an hour left for today. Good job.
